                        `;
                        break;
                    case '2':
                        content = `
                            <h2>Soil and Plant Health Monitoring System</h2>
                            <p><strong>Role:</strong> Handling device components and design, Database management</p>
                            <p>Created a comprehensive monitoring system that tracks soil moisture, nutrient levels, and plant health indicators. The system provides actionable insights for farmers and gardeners.</p>
