                            </ul>
                            <img src="https://placehold.co/600x300/FF6B35/FFFFFF?text=Soil+Health+Monitoring+Details" alt="Project Details" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 1rem;">
                        `;
                        break;
                    case '3':
                        content = `
                            <h2>AI-Powered Contract Analyzer</h2>
                            <p><strong>Role:</strong> AI/ML Implementation</p>
                            <p>Developed during internship at COTHON SOLUTIONS. This tool uses natural language processing and machine learning to analyze legal contracts, identify key clauses, and flag potential issues with improved accuracy.</p>
                            <h3>Technologies Used</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Python</li>
                                <li>Machine Learning</li>
                                <li>Natural Language Processing</li>
                                <li>Data Extraction</li>
                            </ul>
                            <img src="https://placehold.co/600x300/2D3748/FFFFFF?text=AI+Contract+Analyzer+Details" alt="Project Details" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 1rem;">
                        `;
                        break;
                    case 'soil':
                        content = `
                            <h2>Soil and Crop Predicting System</h2>
                            <p><strong>Research Project:</strong> IoT and ML-based agricultural system</p>
                            <p>This system analyzes soil parameters to predict soil type and recommend suitable crops for farmers. It uses multiple sensors to collect data and machine learning algorithms for prediction.</p>
                            <h3>Key Features</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Soil type prediction with 80% accuracy</li>
